										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/fionawarnick/">Fiona Warnick</a></h6>
										Fiona Warnick grew up in Western Massachusetts and holds a BA in Creative Writing from Oberlin College, where she won the Emma Howell Poetry Prize. She teaches preschool in Providence, RI.																			</div>
